history.proof: intros m k x H H0. pose (H1 := @bottom_A m k x H H0). hauto use: not_exd_nil, succ_exd, A_1_A, not_pred_bottom unfold: pred, dart inv: sumbool.

original: intros m k x H H0. pose (H1 := @bottom_A m k x H H0). pose (H2 := @succ_exd m k x H H0). pose (H3 := @cA_eq m k x H). rewrite H3 in *. destruct (succ_dec m k x) as [_ | H4]. - intro H5. apply (f_equal (bottom m k)) in H5. rewrite H5 in H1. rewrite H1 in H0. contradiction. - exfalso. apply H4. apply H0.
